{"tid":332381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[寵物台][有圖] 有冇人知呢隻係咩黎？","createTime":"2017-07-23T03:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T05:26:42.000Z","uid":115206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"519b7b4f1ceb264ff5680a190ffd97e031985795","tid":332381,"uid":115206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"小弟才疏學淺<br />\n請問巴絲打們，知唔知呢隻係咩黎？<br />\n係唔係蜜蜂果類？<br />\n<br />\n夏天就好多隻飛入屋，寵物咁款<br />\n唔小心佢飛左入房就會比冷氣凍瓜左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/111057_4decb5c3793bdfb05be321900913408f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F111057_4decb5c3793bdfb05be321900913408f.JPG&h=5328239a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/111118_1f8a3965b972aad41dffb4dea215a39d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F111118_1f8a3965b972aad41dffb4dea215a39d.JPG&h=bac88358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42658333a2b8c5e4e29c2498abd4b580df635daa","tid":332381,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"樁米？"},{"pid":"e209e71204aa788396426e892a8d5c94c25c651d","tid":332381,"uid":51051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"泥蜂黎"},{"pid":"3f32946997a32a9896bf3e6930ac406d69695f0b","tid":332381,"uid":115206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泥蜂黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我 GOOGLE 圖片見唔多似咁<br />\n係咪有好多個品種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}